  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1072280/extras/1eaf004e8bb3119ad884c55e8786291e.apng?t=1606234756\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1072280/extras/1eaf004e8bb3119ad884c55e8786291e.poster.avif?t=1606234756\" class=\"bb_img\" width=441 height=156 /></picture></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >is a shoot em up  featuring.</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Solo play or up to four player local co-op<br></li><li>Lots a power ups, weapons, and a charge shot<br></li><li>A campaign with seven levels <br></li><li>Huge boss battles<br></li><li>An unlockable Boss Rush mode <br></li><li>Six unique playable ships</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1072280/extras/88da3f0a83500609684def8d62cfa57d.avif?t=1606234756\" width=384 height=256 /></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Now with new retro style shaders!</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1072280/extras/68bb075d97a01a403d0d8f7118827330.poster.avif?t=1606234756\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1072280/extras/68bb075d97a01a403d0d8f7118827330.webm?t=1606234756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1072280/extras/68bb075d97a01a403d0d8f7118827330.mp4?t=1606234756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1072280/extras/779df0f8b8a4f08e394470a27faf9833.poster.avif?t=1606234756\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://